<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Ending With -IZE — Scrabble Suffix Scoring Guide</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The -IZE suffix is a Scrabble powerhouse. With the Z tile worth 10 points on its own, every -IZE word carries serious scoring weight. This verb-forming suffix transforms adjectives and nouns into actions (real→realize, organ→organize) and opens up bingo opportunities that can swing an entire game.</p>

<p>Understanding -IZE patterns lets you exploit one of the highest-value tiles in the bag while creating natural-sounding words that opponents rarely challenge.</p>

<p>Whether you're building from scratch or extending an existing word on the board, -IZE gives you scoring options that few other suffixes can match.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why -IZE Matters in Scrabble</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">12 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">I(1)+Z(10)+E(1) base</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">300+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid -IZE words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4–14</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The Z tile is the second-highest scoring letter in Scrabble (behind Q), and -IZE gives you a reliable, unchallenged way to deploy it. Unlike awkward Q placements, -IZE words feel natural and rarely draw challenges.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring -IZE Words</h2>

